    "Name": "Nyx",
    "Details": "Developed as a super-fast scouting design, the Nyx Prototype is still being put through its paces by the Word of Blake. Designed for high speed and low drag, the Nyx is incredibly fast, able to keep pace with all but the absolute fastest units on the battlefield. Using Endo-Steel, Ferro-Fibrous, and a 300-rated XL fusion engine for weight savings, the Nyx still carries a respectable punch for its size. The NX-65 carries twin ER Small Lasers as well as trio of MML-3s. One ton each of SRM and LRM ammo gives the Nyx reasonable endurance.<br><br>X-class mechs feature upgrades to their armour, thermal management and defensive systems that improve their survivability on the 31st century battlefield.",
